fix(selection-service): CS0122 GetService inaccessible – use IServiceProvider

Date: 2026-03-19
Affects:
  - Services/SelectionService.cs

--- Details ---

Root cause:
  AsyncPackage.GetService(Type) is `protected internal`.
  Calling it from an external service class (SelectionService) triggers CS0122.

Fix:
  Cast the AsyncPackage reference to IServiceProvider (a public interface it implements).
  Store as `private readonly IServiceProvider _serviceProvider = package`.
  Replace _package.GetService(...) → _serviceProvider.GetService(...) at:
    - Line 69:  GetDteSelection()      → typeof(DTE)
    - Line 164: GetActiveWpfTextView() → typeof(SVsTextManager)

  GetServiceAsync() in InitializeAsync() is unaffected (public method on AsyncPackage).


Date: 2026-03-19
Affects:
  - Services/SelectionService.cs (new)
  - ToolWindows/SampleToolWindowState.cs
  - ToolWindows/SampleToolWindowControl.xaml
  - ToolWindows/SampleToolWindowControl.xaml.cs
  - MyPackage.cs
  - AsyncToolWindowSample.csproj

--- Details ---

feat(services): new SelectionService wrapping both VS Selection API tiers

  Tier 1 — DTE TextSelection (COM, 1-based):
    - GetDteSelection()         → raw TextSelection for direct manipulation
    - GetDteCaretInfo()         → DteCaretInfo DTO: Line, Col, Anchor, Active, Mode
    - GotoLine(line, select)    → navigate caret to line
    - SelectAll()               → select all text in active document
    - SelectCurrentLine()       → select current line
    - CollapseSelection()       → collapse to ActivePoint
    - FindText(pattern, case)   → find first match, returns bool

  Tier 2 — IWpfTextView MEF (managed, 0-based):
    - GetActiveWpfTextView()    → IWpfTextView of focused editor pane
    - GetMefCaretInfo()         → MefCaretInfo DTO: Offset, Line, Col, ContentType
    - GetMefSelectedSpans()     → List<SelectionSpanInfo> from SelectedSpans
    - InsertAtCaret(text)       → ITextEdit.Insert at caret position
    - ReplaceSelection(text)    → ITextEdit.Replace on StreamSelectionSpan
    - GetBufferText()           → full snapshot text

  DTOs added: DteCaretInfo, MefCaretInfo, SelectionSpanInfo

  InitializeAsync() resolves IVsEditorAdaptersFactoryService via SComponentModel MEF container.
  All public methods require UI thread (ThreadHelper.ThrowIfNotOnUIThread).

feat(package): wire SelectionService into MyPackage and SampleToolWindowState

  - MyPackage: new Selection property, initialized in InitializeAsync
  - SampleToolWindowState: new Selection property
  - InitializeToolWindowAsync: pass Selection to state object

feat(tool-window): add 9 Selection API demo buttons to SampleToolWindowControl

  DTE group (4 buttons):
    - Show Caret Info (DTE)       → logs DteCaretInfo to Output Window
    - Select Current Line (DTE)   → calls SelectCurrentLine()
    - Find 'TODO' (DTE)           → calls FindText("TODO"), logs result
    - Collapse Selection (DTE)    → calls CollapseSelection()

  MEF group (5 buttons):
    - Show Caret Info (MEF)       → logs MefCaretInfo to Output Window
    - Show Selected Spans (MEF)   → logs all SnapshotSpans
    - Insert Text at Caret (MEF)  → inserts comment placeholder via ITextEdit
    - Replace Selection (MEF)     → wraps selection in comment via ITextEdit
    - Buffer Char Count (MEF)     → counts chars/lines in current buffer

  XAML: added ScrollViewer wrapper; d:DesignHeight 450→720.
  Code-behind: added Truncate() helper to avoid overly long log lines.

build(csproj): add SelectionService compile entry and 4 new managed references

  New <Compile> entry: Services\SelectionService.cs

  New <Reference> entries (resolve via AssemblySearchPaths, no HintPath needed):
    - Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentModelHost  (SComponentModel / IComponentModel)
    - Microsoft.VisualStudio.Editor              (IVsEditorAdaptersFactoryService)
    - Microsoft.VisualStudio.Text.Logic          (ITextEdit)
    - Microsoft.VisualStudio.Text.UI             (ITextView, ITextSelection, ITextCaret)
    - Microsoft.VisualStudio.Text.UI.Wpf         (IWpfTextView)
